  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nWhen [regenerating checkpoint states](https://github.com/PegaSysEng/teku/blob/39bfecad0bff96e5ab31aaca970929f45b61b94d/storage/src/main/java/tech/pegasys/teku/storage/store/Store.java#L495), we should be able to reduce the required work by looking for existing checkpoint states rooted at the same block in our checkpoint cache.  For example, if we need to generate a checkpoint at block A, epoch 3, we can regenerate using an existing checkpoint state at block A, epoch 2.  ",
